# ── Secrets / environment ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Never commit live secrets. .env.example IS tracked (it documents the shape).
**/.env
*.pem
*.key
*secret*
*credential*

# ── Build output ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Maven bundles (the JARs are built from src/ via `mvn clean package`).
**/target/
*.jwa

# ── Generated artefacts (derived; regenerate, don't commit) ──────────────
# Forms/datalists/userviews are generated from the *.spec.yml sources via
# scripts/gen_*.py — the specs are the source of truth, not the output.
**/generated/

# ── Python caches ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc

# ── IDE / OS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
*.iml
.DS_Store

# ── Scratch ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.bak
~$*
